topic.title: Why is there so many chinese people on Zeronet?
topic.body: I haven't been on Zeronet for quite some time, but I see a lot of chinese people using it. Why is that?

1_1LfQ8dwqkqkGQNCg1kBevHPxjvTRJTQYBz.body:
> [akito](#comment_70_1F8omDpXyPsBfd9CBJ91o4Wv1AA2KxqMEY): Obviously, because they live in a restricted country... You can't reach most of the internet without using any VPN or solutions like this one.

True but why Chinese predominately? Why not other censored countries?

1_19imiBWm39vSNQpp9a4y3zwHyasYJsMDp2.body: I use to have a piratebox but no one ever connected to it.
